OL,3,CEx-human rights lawyer sentenced for
OL,4,CIraq war fraud
OL,6,FThe ex-human rights lawyer who
OL,7,Frepresented clients against Iraq War
OL,8,Fveterans has avoided jail after being
OL,9,Ffound guilty of fraud.
OL,11,FThe charges relate to Phil Shiner,
OL,12,Ffrom Birmingham, application in 2007
OL,13,Ffor up to #200,000 of legal aid for
OL,14,Fhis firm Public Interest Lawyers.
OL,16,FJudge Christopher Hehir said "although
OL,17,Fthere was obvious dishonesty", he did
OL,18,Fnot think the former lawyer was
OL,19,F"motivated by personal greed".
