OL,3,CEx-human rights lawyer sentenced for
OL,4,CIraq war fraud
OL,6,FHe prosecuted one of the few
OL,7,Fsuccessful cases against a British
OL,8,Fofficer. In 2007, a soldier from the
OL,9,FQueen's Lancashire Regiment was jailed
OL,10,Ffor a year in connection with the
OL,11,Fdeath of Iraqi civilian Baha Mousa in
OL,12,FSeptember 2003.
OL,14,FBaha Mousa, an Iraqi hotel
OL,15,Freceptionist, died with 93 injuries in
OL,16,FBritish army custody in Basra.
OL,18,FHuman rights groups Liberty and
OL,19,FJustice named Shiner Lawyer of the
OL,20,FYear in 2004.
