OL,3,CEx-human rights lawyer sentenced for
OL,4,CIraq war fraud
OL,6,FThe Al-Sweady Inquiry
OL,8,FHis firm was central in the Iraq
OL,9,FHistoric Allegations Team's (IHAT)
OL,10,Finvestigations into the conduct of
OL,11,FBritish officers during the Iraq war.
OL,12,F65% of all the cases they investigated
OL,13,Fwere brought from his firm.
OL,15,FShiner's most high-profile case led to
OL,16,Fthe Al-Sweady Inquiry - which focused
OL,17,Fon claims that British soldiers
OL,18,Fmurdered 20 Iraqis and abused nine
OL,19,Fothers at their Camp Abu Naji base.
