OL,6,FHamid Al-Sweady's, whose name the
OL,7,Finquiry bore, was one of the soldiers
OL,8,Fkilled in the fighting.
OL,10,FThe claims came out after a firefight
OL,11,Fbetween UK soldiers at an Iraqi
OL,12,Fmilitia known as the Battle of Danny
OL,13,FBoy at a UK checkpoint on 14 May 2004.
