OL,6,FThe fallout from Al-Sweady inquiries'
OL,7,Ffindings
OL,9,FShiner was struck off as a solicitor
OL,10,Fin 2017 at a tribunal after being
OL,11,Ffound guilty of misconduct and
OL,12,Fdishonesty relating to false abuse
OL,13,Fclaims against British troops in the
OL,14,FAl-Sweady inquiry.
OL,16,FAfter he was struck off, all cases his
OL,17,Ffirm pursued as part of the IHAT were
OL,18,Freassessed. Some of the cases
OL,19,Foriginally brought by Shiner's firm
OL,20,Fwere found to be credible.
