OL,6,FThese included two civil cases
OL,7,Finvolving four Iraqis alleging
OL,8,Fmistreatment in British detention.
OL,10,FIn 2018, a judge found the allegations
OL,11,Fto be "credible" and ruled that
OL,12,Fsoldiers had breached the Geneva
OL,13,FConventions. The Iraqis were awarded
OL,14,Ftens of thousands of pounds in damages.
OL,16,FOverall, the Ministry of Defence has
OL,17,Fpaid out a total of more than #20
OL,18,Fmillion in compensation settlements
OL,19,Ffor abuse claims from Iraqi nationals.
